   Example 2

   The following:
begin
;
;  Diamond shape, counterclockwise ordering letting the code create a
;  closed polygon by adding a final vertex that equals the first.
;
  order = gc_clkwise((/ 0.0, -1.0,  0.0,  1.0/), \
                     (/-3.0, -2.0, -1.0, -2.0/) )
  print(order)
end

   produces:

